Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:50.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] Lulu, I failed you\Nas a friend, and I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.22,0:00:54.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I knew how you felt,\Nbut pretended not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.43,0:00:57.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I lied to you, even though\Nyou were my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.06,0:01:01.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's too late now,\Nbut I want you to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.94,0:01:05.81,Main,,0,0,0,,This is what happened the day\NI let go of Kureha's love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.90,0:01:08.94,Main,,0,0,0,,and this is why I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.03,0:01:14.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO, LULU]\NYurikuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.41,0:01:16.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurikuma Arashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.84,0:02:53.67,Main,,0,0,0,,[CUB SOLDIER M]\NNo way she's not done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.76,0:02:55.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[CUB SOLDIER N]\NEither way, she'd slow us down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:02:56.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's exclude her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.01,0:03:00.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[CUB SOLDIERS] Exclude her.\NExclude her. Exclude her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:04.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] I had prepared myself\Nfor that day, and so I was
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.93,0:03:09.94,Main,,0,0,0,,ready to die there, all alone,\Nwithout anyone ever finding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:13.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NBut then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.44,0:03:14.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.53,0:03:17.57,Main,,0,0,0,,It's okay. You and\NI can be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.66,0:03:20.82,Main,,0,0,0,,So you don't have\Nto be alone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.33,0:03:23.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.87,0:03:27.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NDid you know, you and me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:29.71,Main,,0,0,0,,are gonna be together\Nforever, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:32.75,Main,,0,0,0,,My mom told me\Nthat's what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.84,0:03:34.63,Main,,0,0,0,,As long as you\Ndon't forget love,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:38.01,Main,,0,0,0,,you'll never, ever be alone,\Nand if you don't give up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:40.34,Main,,0,0,0,,on love, even if\Nyou lose something,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:42.60,Main,,0,0,0,,you won't be invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.56,0:03:45.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NGrowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:53.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna protect you.\NI promise you I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.36,0:03:56.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:09.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\NIs your love the real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.50,0:04:11.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NGrowl?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:21.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:24.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[REIA]\NKureha? Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:27.73,Main,,0,0,0,,--Where are you, honey?\N--[GINKO grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.48,0:04:31.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] I am not\Ngoing to forget love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.02,0:04:35.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I am not going to\Ngive up on love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:36.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.24,0:04:41.70,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NWe will never be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:43.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.32,0:04:46.37,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NWe will be friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:52.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] After that, Kureha and I\Nbecame the best of friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:05:02.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] We shared so many\Nthings with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.68,0:05:06.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Love was sweet, and kind, and\Nmade everything seem to sparkle
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.06,0:05:10.48,Main,,0,0,0,,like the brightest\Nstar in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:15.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I was so happy, but ended\Nup getting the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:18.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought the world\Nhad approved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.74,0:05:28.37,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA, GINKO awed breaths]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:29.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NBut then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.75,0:05:32.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL A]\NThere's that stinky traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.21,0:05:36.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NUh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.21,0:05:37.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NNo, stay in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.67,0:05:39.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL A] I heard you're\Nhanging out with a bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.92,0:05:41.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Another girl saw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:43.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL B]\NThat's so not cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:45.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Um, I dunno what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:47.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL A]\NDon't play dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:50.35,Main,,0,0,0,,My mommy says bears are gross\Nand dirty and our enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.43,0:05:51.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL C]\NBears are evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.89,0:05:54.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone knows we\Ngotta exclude them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:55.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NThat's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.40,0:05:57.73,Main,,0,0,0,,W-We can be friends with bears.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.82,0:05:59.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, are you defending them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.32,0:06:00.44,Main,,0,0,0,,That's so not cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.53,0:06:02.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL C]\NYou must be evil, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.40,0:06:04.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL A]\NExclude! Exclude!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:07.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRLS]\NExclude! Exclude! Exclude!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.66,0:06:11.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL A] Hey guys, she's an\Nevil girl who defends bears.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:15.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRLS] Exclude! Exclude!\NExclude! Exclude!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.71,0:06:17.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.84,0:06:21.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRLS] Exclude! Exclude!\NExclude! Exclude!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.47,0:06:31.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL A] We have to\Nexclude all traitors!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.14,0:06:37.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NPlease, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.61,0:06:45.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO whimpers]\NGrowl?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:53.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NGrowl. Kureha got hurt for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:57.25,Main,,0,0,0,,This happened to her\Nbecause I'm a bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.33,0:07:01.88,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not okay for\Nme to be a bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:04.80,Main,,0,0,0,,If... If I were a human girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.88,0:07:07.55,Main,,0,0,0,,would we be able to\Nbe together forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.63,0:07:10.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Would I be able\Nto protect Kureha?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.51,0:07:13.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, Lady Kumaria, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.02,0:07:15.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:18.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[bell tolls]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.27,0:07:20.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY]\NIs your love the real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.31,0:07:24.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, your honor, my love's\Nthe real thing. Growl, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:28.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY]\NThis court is now in session!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:33.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY]\NWelcome to Severance Court.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.50,0:07:35.79,Main,,0,0,0,,The door has opened,\Nso enter what we consider
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:38.38,Main,,0,0,0,,the land of enlightenment\Nfor all living things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.46,0:07:40.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, even human and bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.83,0:07:45.30,Main,,0,0,0,,We shall now pass judgment for\Nthe sake of humans and bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.38,0:07:48.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Life Sexy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:51.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Life Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.18,0:07:53.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Life Beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.43,0:07:57.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] Is this where\NLady Kumaria lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:07:59.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY]\NLady Kumaria has been lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:03.90,Main,,0,0,0,,She became meteors that were\Nscattered throughout our planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:05.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.11,0:08:07.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY]\NLet the Yuri Trial begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.65,0:08:10.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Defendant bear, Ginko Yurishiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.32,0:08:11.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Is there anything\Nyou wish to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.03,0:08:16.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl. Yes, I wanna be with\NKureha forever, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.41,0:08:17.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to protect her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.96,0:08:22.75,Main,,0,0,0,,So please say yes. I wish for\Nyou to make me a human girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.25,0:08:28.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY] Very well.\NHowever, there is one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:31.18,Main,,0,0,0,,To become human,\Nyou must let your love go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:33.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Which means, she will\Nforget all about you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.97,0:08:35.31,Main,,0,0,0,,and the love you share.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.39,0:08:37.14,Main,,0,0,0,,And on top of that, you're\Nnot allowed to tell anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.23,0:08:38.68,Main,,0,0,0,,what happened here, or else!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.77,0:08:40.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's just like\NThe Little Mermaid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:42.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Sparkle, sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.44,0:08:43.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:45.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[SEXY]\NWhen Kureha Tsubaki wakes up,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.90,0:08:48.49,Main,,0,0,0,,she will most likely reject you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.57,0:08:50.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Reject me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.49,0:08:52.37,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:59.66,Main,,0,0,0,,It's... It's a bear!\NStay away from me! Someone help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.75,0:09:01.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:05.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.59,0:09:11.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] That's right, Lulu. To\Nget my wish to be a human girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.51,0:09:17.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I had to let go of Kureha.\NI had to let go of her love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.64,0:09:18.89,Main,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.52,0:09:22.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[REIA] Someday, I promise,\Nthe time will come
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:25.19,Main,,0,0,0,,when bears and people\Ncan be friends forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.61,0:09:31.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] I was sent\Nback to the bear world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:38.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, Ginko. Do you still insist\Nyou love this filthy human girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.29,0:09:40.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, I refuse to\Ngive up on love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:42.41,Main,,0,0,0,,--Growl, growl!\N--[CUBS murmur]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:43.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Utterly dreadful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.92,0:09:47.09,Main,,0,0,0,,You are hereby no longer\Nconsidered a cub of Kumaria.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.17,0:09:49.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Be gone, Ginko the\NLone Wolfsbane,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.55,0:09:51.26,Main,,0,0,0,,and blight on this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.34,0:09:55.18,Main,,0,0,0,,For you are a sinful child\Nwho has betrayed our Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.14,0:10:00.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY] You must wait.\NThe time will eventually come
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.31,0:10:03.10,Main,,0,0,0,,when you will find\NKureha Tsubaki again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.19,0:10:04.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE BEAUTY]\NAnd, if you can find a way
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.81,0:10:08.65,Main,,0,0,0,,to become friends with her\Nonce more. Sparkle, sparkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:10.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NMy wish will come true?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.49,0:10:11.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE COOL]\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.65,0:10:13.70,Main,,0,0,0,,You must exchange Promise\NKisses with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.78,0:10:15.99,Main,,0,0,0,,As long as you do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:18.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] ...I can become\Na human girl, growl?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.08,0:10:23.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY] Now, defendant\Nbear Ginko Yurishiro, I ask you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:27.92,Main,,0,0,0,,will you become human?\NOr, will you give up on love?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:30.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] I'll never give\Nup on love, Your Honor,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:33.63,Main,,0,0,0,,so I'll become human.\NGrowl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.02,0:10:45.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] I waited and waited\Nfor the time to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.24,0:10:54.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NAnd then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:11:00.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\N...I met you, Lulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.13,0:11:08.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:09.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY]\NIs your love the real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.04,0:11:12.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Absolutely. Growl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.59,0:11:14.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY]\NThe Invisible Storm has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:17.55,Main,,0,0,0,,The time has finally come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:22.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] I understand, and I\Nwill never give up on love!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:24.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu's not gonna give\Nup on love, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.64,0:11:28.19,Main,,0,0,0,,She'll support love. Ginko.\NLulu will always be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.27,0:11:29.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NYou were true to your word,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.56,0:11:32.48,Main,,0,0,0,,and stayed by my side\Nno matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.57,0:11:38.41,Main,,0,0,0,,You gave me love without seeking\Nanything in return. Lulu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.49,0:11:40.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.58,0:11:41.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:44.00,Main,,0,0,0,,We're gonna be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,0:11:46.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu will protect you,\Nand help get your love!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.83,0:11:52.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, ready? Let's go to\Nthe human world! Growl, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.48,0:12:09.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] From the beginning,\Nwe hated you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.19,0:12:13.61,Main,,0,0,0,,but also, we loved you from\Nthe beginning, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.69,0:12:16.78,Main,,0,0,0,,And so, I became\Na human girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.86,0:12:20.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha, all I wanted was to\Nbecome true friends with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.74,0:12:23.20,Main,,0,0,0,,So, I had to cross the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:26.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[sniffs] She's here!\NAnd you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.71,0:12:28.83,Main,,0,0,0,,She really does smell delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:31.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NLulu. From the very beginning,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.63,0:12:33.88,Main,,0,0,0,,you were my true friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.72,0:12:44.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHOUKO] Okay. We way\Nknow the problem, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.43,0:12:47.02,Main,,0,0,0,,We have to exclude, like,\Nboth of those bears lurking
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:50.98,Main,,0,0,0,,in our school! Is everyone,\Nlike, totally ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.06,0:12:53.48,Main,,0,0,0,,So we're gonna, like,\Nconfirm this one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.57,0:12:56.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Who should we way use\Nas bait for the bear?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.65,0:12:59.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's search sacrifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.43,0:13:26.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:27.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.69,0:13:36.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO] Would you like me\Nto lick your wounds for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.15,0:13:37.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I would not. Growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.78,0:13:41.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, great. You're gonna make me\Nwork for it today, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.28,0:13:44.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on now, Ginko.\NDon't be that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:46.41,Main,,0,0,0,,We both want Kureha, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.49,0:13:50.29,Main,,0,0,0,,No one can deny a\Ndesire this powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:53.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's find her and eat\Nher. You know you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.33,0:13:56.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Couldn't you breathe in that\Ndelicious smell forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.34,0:13:59.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I love the scent of a girl who\Nrefuses to back down on love.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.01,0:14:02.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Delicious smell. Grr.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.09,0:14:06.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.39,0:14:09.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps, screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:16.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO]\NNicely done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.82,0:14:19.78,Main,,0,0,0,,These girls need to\Nlearn their lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.86,0:14:23.32,Main,,0,0,0,,A hunter is always in danger\Nof becoming the hunted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:26.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NGrowl, growl, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.12,0:14:27.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT B screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.62,0:14:28.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NGrowl, growl, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.58,0:14:29.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT C screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.08,0:14:31.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NGrowl, growl, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.16,0:14:32.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT D screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.55,0:14:45.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:50.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[UKO] This is the Bear-Killing\NBeam Truck reporting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.14,0:14:51.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Target Alpha has been sighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:55.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Now preparing to fire\NEco-Kumagical Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:14:57.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONOMI-BOT]\NNasty?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.06,0:15:00.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Buzz, buzz, buzz! Nasty, nasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.07,0:15:06.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Energy is replenishing. We'll\Nbe at full power in, 10, 9, 8...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.91,0:15:13.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONOMI-BOT] Nasty, nasty,\Nnasty, nasty. nasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.13,0:15:21.42,Main,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:23.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHOUKO] Wow, they're,\Nlike, still wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:24.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't believe\Nshe way just tried
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:27.72,Main,,0,0,0,,to take her\Nbait like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:31.68,Main,,0,0,0,,So, how did you, like, tame her?\NLike, did you tell her you loved
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:34.31,Main,,0,0,0,,her and then give\Nher a little kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:37.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHOUKO chuckles]\NYou, like, way disgust me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:38.90,Main,,0,0,0,,[beep]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.98,0:15:41.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[UKO] This is Bear-Killing Beam\NTruck. We fired on Target Alpha
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:44.82,Main,,0,0,0,,and did manage to scratch her,\Nbut unfortunately she got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.90,0:15:45.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHOUKO]\NDamn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:47.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAREN]\NThis is D-Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.24,0:15:50.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I've been informed that the\Ndoor in the lily bed is open.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.45,0:15:52.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm heading that way\Nto investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.41,0:15:55.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I was right, they're using\Nthat place as their gateway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.66,0:15:59.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Wily bears. Oh, yeah.\NI have something fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.25,0:16:02.25,Main,,0,0,0,,When I, like, searched your\Nhouse, I totally found this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.34,0:16:03.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NThe book!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:05.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Your mommy, like,\Nwrote this, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.01,0:16:09.26,Main,,0,0,0,,A bear and a human becoming\Nfriends? I bet writing this crap
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.34,0:16:12.97,Main,,0,0,0,,is, like, way what got her\Nkilled by those bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.06,0:16:14.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.43,0:16:17.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHOUKO] "Lady Kumaria"?\NWhat are you, like, stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.14,0:16:22.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHOUKO] There are no gods in\Nthis world. The only thing like,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:26.15,Main,,0,0,0,,ruling us is the invisible,\Nlike, atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:29.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.16,0:16:32.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHOUKO]\NHere, beary, beary, beary!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:36.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I have your food, like,\Nwaiting right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.47,0:16:49.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO] That was a\Nclose one, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.76,0:16:52.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, when did they get\Nthat barbaric weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.43,0:16:55.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, what d'ya say?\NShall we go eat Kureha, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.64,0:16:57.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Like you can help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.35,0:17:00.02,Main,,0,0,0,,The desire to completely\Nmonopolize another is stronger
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:02.06,Main,,0,0,0,,than anything in\Nthe world, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.15,0:17:03.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[footsteps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.27,0:17:05.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I told you.\NI won't forget love.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.03,0:17:08.53,Main,,0,0,0,,And, I won't give up on love.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:10.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONOMI-BOT]\NNasty. Nasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:13.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[UKO]\NUh... Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.24,0:17:15.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONOMI-BOT]\NNa... sty...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.08,0:17:18.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] I've finally\Nfound the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.08,0:17:19.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I refuse to let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:21.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Um, what are you\Ntalking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.71,0:17:25.92,Main,,0,0,0,,You've already accepted me,\Nsilly. Did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.00,0:17:29.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] The thing about love is.\NIt won't be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:31.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Not by a storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:35.31,Main,,0,0,0,,True love is much\Nstronger than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.39,0:17:38.31,Main,,0,0,0,,And it would never\Nleave me all alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:46.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] I can hear her.\NIt's the same as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:48.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha's calling me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:50.36,Main,,0,0,0,,When I was separated\Nfrom the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:52.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha was the only\None to find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.95,0:17:56.20,Main,,0,0,0,,She gave me love, and I didn't\Neven have to ask for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.28,0:17:58.74,Main,,0,0,0,,So this time, I'll be\Nthe one to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.83,0:18:00.04,Main,,0,0,0,,No, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.50,0:18:04.58,Main,,0,0,0,,You can't do that. Don't you\Nknow you're still a bear,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.67,0:18:07.09,Main,,0,0,0,,or have you forgotten\Nthe reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:09.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I am your desire,\Nwhich is true love.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:12.42,Main,,0,0,0,,And I am more powerful\Nthan anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.05,0:18:16.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NYou're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.64,0:18:20.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Desire is nothing, but for true\Nlove, I'll leap into the storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:22.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:26.23,Main,,0,0,0,,You really think\Nyou can abandon me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:28.61,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not possible!\NI'm your desire,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.69,0:18:30.40,Main,,0,0,0,,you can't walk away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:37.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait! A beast who loses\Nher desire will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.25,0:18:43.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NGoodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.42,0:18:54.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I will tear my image to shreds!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.43,0:18:58.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.39,0:19:05.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Silly girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.32,0:19:13.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha. I've found you.\NGrowl, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.95,0:19:16.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NStay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:17.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.99,0:19:22.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't come any closer\Nto me. Just stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.24,0:19:24.37,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you want with\Nme at this point?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.46,0:19:27.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Everything that's\Nhappened is your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.26,0:19:35.92,Main,,0,0,0,,From the beginning,\Nwe never should've been friends
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.01,0:19:38.22,Main,,0,0,0,,because humans and bears\Nhave been severed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:40.68,Main,,0,0,0,,We can't be together\Nno matter what we do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.76,0:19:43.35,Main,,0,0,0,,So you say, growl. But still,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.43,0:19:45.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to become\Nyour friend again,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.31,0:19:48.61,Main,,0,0,0,,and there's nothing\Nanyone can do to stop us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.69,0:19:50.27,Main,,0,0,0,,After we become\Nfriends like before,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.36,0:19:52.44,Main,,0,0,0,,we'll be able to share\Na Promise Kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.53,0:19:56.65,Main,,0,0,0,,That's all we'll have to do\Nto make me human forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.74,0:19:58.24,Main,,0,0,0,,As long as you\Ndon't forget love,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:19:59.82,Main,,0,0,0,,you'll never,\Never be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.91,0:20:02.74,Main,,0,0,0,,And if you don't give up, then\Neven if you lose something,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.83,0:20:04.29,Main,,0,0,0,,you won't be invisible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.37,0:20:07.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:10.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Shut up! It's your\Nfault everyone died!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.38,0:20:13.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Even Sumika!\NI won't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.63,0:20:16.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll never forgive\Nany of you bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.43,0:20:21.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop this. Just go to\Nthe other side, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:24.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I already sent Lulu back through\Nthe Door of Friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.06,0:20:28.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Go to her, and never\Nreturn here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.53,0:20:37.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NDon't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.36,0:20:40.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko! Stay away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.32,0:20:41.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.91,0:20:43.99,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't stop. I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.08,0:20:45.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll never back down on love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.62,0:20:46.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.21,0:20:52.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA] Kureha, I'll never\Nback down on my love, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:57.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA cries] No. I don't\Nwanna lose anyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.61,0:21:22.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:26.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.83,0:21:33.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu's sorry, Kure-pie,\Nbut she had to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.88,0:21:35.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA cries]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.63,0:21:41.43,Main,,0,0,0,,He, he. Oh, Kure-pie,\Nyou're such a bad liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.51,0:21:44.18,Main,,0,0,0,,No! Lulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.26,0:21:48.10,Main,,0,0,0,,She let Lulu escape, said\NLulu wasn't her friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.18,0:21:52.27,Main,,0,0,0,,But her lie was, it was\Nsuper-duper obvious to Lulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.35,0:21:55.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko. Lulu knows\Nit will work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.48,0:22:00.15,Main,,0,0,0,,She knows it. Kure-pie\Nis going to forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.24,0:22:04.99,Main,,0,0,0,,No, that's not true. Mm-mm.\NShe already has forgiven you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.08,0:22:06.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.62,0:22:10.12,Main,,0,0,0,,You can finally be her friend,\NGinko. Isn't that wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.20,0:22:15.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Make your love come true, okay?\NYou can get a Promise Kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.75,0:22:18.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu believes it.\NShe believes in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.67,0:22:23.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Here, Lulu collected\Nthis, it's your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.85,0:22:31.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu is so clever,\Nisn't she? Growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.74,0:22:43.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.11,0:22:44.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.49,0:22:54.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu, no. Lulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.05,0:24:28.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY]\NDefendant human Kureha Tsubaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.97,0:24:32.60,Main,,0,0,0,,are you ready to\Nadmit your crime?
